接口 DataOwnedEffect

    Interface DataOwnedEffect. Effects that owns data field

    khjxiaogu file: DataOwnedEffect.java time: 2020年8月4日

    • 方法详细资料

      • initEffect

        void initEffect​(org.bukkit.entity.Player p,
                int time,
                int level)
        添加效果时呼叫此函数 called when this effect is given to the player.
        参数:
        p - 目标玩家 target player
        time - 时间
        level - 等级

      • onDoDamage

        void onDoDamage​(org.bukkit.event.entity.EntityDamageByEntityEvent ev)
        有此效果的玩家攻击时呼叫 called when a player with this effect attacks others.
        参数:
        ev - 攻击事件 attack event

      • onBeDamagedByEntity

        void onBeDamagedByEntity​(org.bukkit.event.entity.EntityDamageByEntityEvent ev)
        有此效果的玩家遭到实体攻击时呼叫 called when a player with this effect attacked by an entity.
        参数:
        ev - 受击事件 attack event

      • onBeDamaged

        void onBeDamaged​(org.bukkit.event.entity.EntityDamageEvent ev)
        有此效果的玩家受到伤害时呼叫，被实体攻击时也会呼叫。 called when a player with this effect being damaged,would also called if damaged by an entity.
        参数:
        ev - 受伤事件 damage event

      • onTick

        void onTick()
        每5tick呼叫一次，此呼叫为非同步呼叫，如果需要操作，请用BukkitRunnable.runTask并进行操作 called asynchronously per 5 ticks.if any synchronous operation is needed,please schedule a synchronous event.

      • onEnd

        void onEnd​(boolean timeout)
        效果失效时呼叫 called when this effect expires .
        参数:
        timeout - true if it is removed by time out 是否因为超时被移除

      • getEffectIdentifier

        java.lang.String getEffectIdentifier()
        获取该效果的名字 returns identifier of this effect,must be unique.
        返回:
        效果名字 identifier of the effect

      • getExecutionPriority

        SkillPriority getExecutionPriority()
        获取该技能的效果事件执行时间.设置为0则不执行 returns the event execution time in bukkit of damage events,returns null indicates that this effect has no damage events
        返回:
        执行顺序/execution order
